milestones.description: Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs, going past Barry Wood's 2
Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches (3) in ODIs for ENG, going past Barry Wood's 2
Geoff Boycott has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7) for ENG, going past Fletcher
Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for ENG, going past Barry Wood's 2
Elliott has broken the record for officiating the most ODIs (3) as an umpire, going past Constant
Geoff Boycott has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (7), going past Fletcher
Tony Greig has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs, going past Barry Wood's 2
Mike Denness and Tony Greig's 48-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 39 between Fletcher and Barry Wood
Tony Greig and Chris Old's 14-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 11 between Tony Greig and Barry Wood
